data.description: Price Improvement!! Seller is Motivated!!! Fully Renovated Ranch Home with Finished Basement! Open Kitchen Concept all new soft closed drawers+cabinets, new flooring, granite, exposed shelving Opens to Dining Area that boasts fireplace great for entertainment. Added Mud Room Area comes with washer/dryer, room for desk/office area. New Roof, New Interior Paint, Quality Luxury flooring throughout, like new thick carpet, bright natural sunlight. Master on the main has walk-in closet, fully renovated bathroom floor to ceiling tile.   All secondary bedrooms are spacious with large closet space. Secondary bathroom has been updated with beautiful floor to ceiling tile, has been updated with double vanity. Basement finished with bonus room, family room, storage and utility room. Exit to the exterior patio overlooking beautiful private 1.8 acres. Come take a look and make an offer today!!!
